&lt;p&gt;#2023. 11. 4. 20:19&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/7cb78bfc-9d3e-44c6-bc19-6286428d84c1" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;금요일 약대 최종 미팅까지 마치고.. 커피사서 연구실 돌아가는길&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="828" height="1087" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/22ffe9e1-e83c-4209-aada-15abd08180fa" /&gt;
