&lt;img width="1280" height="1280" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8a04b8ee-08b8-44ed-bb45-3f6434827f78" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;마고플레인 가서 스콘시켜놓구 낭낭한 혼공 ㅎㅎ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1280" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8a7d85a8-94d3-4d03-a70c-32df47e01844" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;익숙한간식이아닌 새로운간식 히히&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1280" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/cd47c2fd-f514-44ae-b0b7-99c7a2f4eb25" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;아침에 그시절우리가좋아했던소녀 보면서 김치사발면 먹고(조금 남겼음)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1280" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d88ebc5a-71d2-43f7-93e6-c2c19e888ad5" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;새로운 스벅에서 미친듯이 데이터 뽑기&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1280" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d1f3a88a-331e-412a-8cdd-9ed98fbac350" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;달달한거 먹고싶던 타이밍에 먹어보라고줬다 ㅎㅋ 운좋다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1280" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a16ec0b9-fd96-438e-be79-664e88f3baf4" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1050" height="1050" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e98f5b2e-9154-41e2-9085-2d3d5ff218d8" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;엄마아빠랑 여행왔다 ㅎㅎ 예쁜 카페도 가고&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1280" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ebafaa34-82ab-4623-bcff-dd00ab34c15a" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1280" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/6746cfd9-9e27-4352-8056-38a23afff4ce" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;와인도 마셨다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;적당한 가라앉음을 유지하자 나는 불행을이겨내는건 익숙한데 행복을 잠재우는건 어려운거같아&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>방학끝자락</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2023/23blog12/</link><pubDate>Fri, 25 Aug 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2023/23blog12/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="방학끝자락"&gt;
